Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get crackin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:03.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's-a-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:05.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:33.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw a shooting star the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:38.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Kagami said something about the\Nwishing three times thing being unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.55,0:01:40.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:43.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:45.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to see the stars from our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:46.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since your house is in the city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:50.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would probably be too amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:52.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to have time to make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of a dazzling, shining star...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:58.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...would fill you with feelings of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That could explain the myth that shooting stars grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:06.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your honesty is what dazzles me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:09.33,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(206,198)}The Many Ways\Nto Spend\NChristmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:11.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:13.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have finals first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any plans for winter break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:18.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't taken a vacation in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:23.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Asakusa the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:25.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you get sleepy on the train during winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She missed her stop?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:31.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that the opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The train reached the end of the line and turned around...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:38.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then I missed my stop again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:40.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I was conscious, we were in Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:41.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:45.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only miss your stop so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't entirely a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I hadn't visited Asakusa in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't be doing that right before finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.05,0:03:00.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I had a feeling I saw a girl in a\Nsailor uniform with a machine gun walk by...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me someone was making a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:06.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:08.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping more helps you grow more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're growing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:11.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an even better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad pulled an all-nighter and then went to turn in a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He got on an early-morning train but missed his stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...then it reached the end and made a U-turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and when he woke up, he'd already missed his stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this happened a few more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:27.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He started to wake up when he got close to his station...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he still ended up missing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.39,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Patrasche...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:29.85,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I'm so tired...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:34.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was tired and wanted to get\Nhome and sleep, but he couldn't get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he no longer knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:43.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which direction he was going whenever he woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:48.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I still wake up before my stop when I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she has an internal alarm clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:55.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it doesn't work all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's always snacking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:03:59.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But train seats are really warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you get really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all warm and fuzzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...like you're sitting next to the window in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...on a sunny winter afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:12.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Covering for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:17.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tried to wake you up on the ride home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just five more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:27.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She yelled out half-asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around us was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:33.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my friends did that in class once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Birds of a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're grouping us together?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you went to wake someone up\Nand they were like, give me another hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't you be pissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:50.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but five minutes comes up in a lot of other situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, just wait five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe 'cause it isn't too long or too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the five-minute wait for a train feels really long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:06.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People who say to wait five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...tend to make you wait a lot longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how people say to not use\Nyour cell or put on makeup on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a lot worse when the person next to you leans on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you end up wanting to stand after managing to get a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:28.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you're stuck with the sticky head of an old person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:31.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I try to shove them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:36.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they somehow manage to\Nkeep returning to the same position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:38.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:44.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and there's a man on one side and an empty seat on the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I try to lean myself towards the empty seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:50.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but for some reason, I always end up leaning the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:54.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess your body feels more comfortable leaning a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see someone leaning over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:06:00.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I shrink up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:02.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...then their elbow hits my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean they're actually awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:07.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:08.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...some people at our school take the inbound train home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and some people take the outbound train home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:22.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the ones who take the\Ninbound train look more refined somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:23.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Yuki-chan's an inbounder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:25.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:26.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:29.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the farm, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:52.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the stop before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:05.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get any studying done yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:09.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually put in a lot of effort this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How much studying did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Only four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.41,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}A whole four hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:21.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at everything, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do a lot of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:29.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely really competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's my pride as the older sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:36.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I have to be ahead of Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:39.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I usually say neither of us is really older or younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be pretty worried about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tsukasa probably wasn't much competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:47.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stupid Kona-chan thinks she's all that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what my present will be this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:56.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still get presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long did you believe in Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Claus isn't real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:05.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Holy cow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa never came to Konata's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:12.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so her dad gave her presents in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:15.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she thought he might be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He really wants to look good in front of his daughter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the handout from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:24.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Hiiragi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:31.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:34.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the handout from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:37.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sebastian, like. stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:43.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I go to Tsukasa's class a little too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My cavity started hurting recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:52.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't stand dentists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to see the dentist for your cavity the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:04.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentists take a long time on each tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they have to repeat the procedure for every tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it takes a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I ended up escaping...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...after making a number of excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She sounded all cutesy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:18.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but that's pretty crazy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go wild with everyone on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have plans for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:27.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:29.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:33.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:36.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Dad that I'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell.me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.66,0:09:39.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going on a date with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:42.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm just working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost all the customers are male so I wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought you'd managed to get ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a special event on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We dress like Santa CIaus for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love that kind of stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:05.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys also cosplay as shrine maidens for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At your temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that Santa Claus gives everyone presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:17.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but ever since I was little, I was like, he's totally trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:20.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't look down on something based on a holy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiteful brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:22.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:29.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa is supposed to give children dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so what's with the men who turn to this squirt with their dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just casually insulted a lot of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And is it okay for you guys to celebrate Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:39.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We usually got Christmas presents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We worship every god there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We regularly visit temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we sang in a church choir once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:55.59,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:11:00.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A shrine maiden said she wanted\Nto get married in a wedding dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:05.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be a little complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting chilly these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:19.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:25.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something odd about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing odd at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:31.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:36.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why cops are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't you a cop yourself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd someone have to call now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:44.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're about to reveal the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:45.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:46.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the killer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No use in hiding it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:54.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why these two-hour\Nshows always end on the edge of a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:59.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe cause people aren't willing to\Nact until their back's against the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui, evenin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha watchin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A movie for a popular detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimes don't happen in conference rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They happen at the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:16.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody ever gets that passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet you reject that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:24.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the receipts were stolen at the behest of the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why he fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:28.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:29.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:31.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They eat pork bowls a lot in police shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:33.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but apparently, that isn't actually allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so a lot of it's probably made-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:40.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So police commissioners' granddaughters aren't really like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Police commissioners' granddaughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've never met one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd at least want Mai-chan to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To give me hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:49.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Empty dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:54.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of cases with adults going after children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:59.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you teach kids martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't there be a decrease in that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After intensive training...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:08.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Master Oyama was able to beat a\Ncow with his bare hands, with one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And bears toppled like trees after a couple of hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:16.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't that come back to haunt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:18.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When those kids grow up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the adults will be strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People say training in the martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...helps you mature as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:34.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who does martial\Narts and hasn't matured right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:35.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:42.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this cousin, Cousin Yui's little\N sister, who's entering high school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's physically weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:46.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she's sweet and pure and really adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.72,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Cousin Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:53.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I start thinking about how a\Nhealthy spirit leads to a healthy body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:58.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,....I start feeling like something dark\Nis lurking behind those shining eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:01.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt aphorisms are universal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The year's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:07.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's December, you always feel like the year flew by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:12.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to help out at your\Ntemple as shrine maidens again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:15.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come draw your fortune again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With fortunes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:20.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get really bad luck, it's an unpleasant feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you get really good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:24.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it feels like you already wasted your luck for the year, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:28.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's why people say average luck is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here's an early present from your teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your report cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.70,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Here! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:37.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this present!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:43.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We give presents based on effort in my school of Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Think on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bonus to your winter homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:51.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of Christmas cakes will be good this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to a bakery...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are so many cute cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:57.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you can have fun just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:00.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to the cakes that weren't sold before Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:04.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the employees take them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:08.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if nobody takes them, they might throw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:12.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They often compare marriage to Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how twenty-five is the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:18.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're past twenty-five, a Christmas cake is just another cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After one night, it's just another decorated cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that suddenly looks stale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:24.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you lose your appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:28.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about Santa Claus with Kona-chan the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long did you believe in Santa, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:35.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like you would have been a true believer like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also believed in Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:41.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I tried to send a\Nletter of gratitude to Santa Claus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and did some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:47.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't learn much after asking my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I did some thorough investigating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and learned of the people Santa Claus was based on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:54.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and once I saw the phrase "origin of Santa Claus" pop up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:57.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...my dreams were quickly shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you do, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:01.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you would expect from Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:09.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little pissed about losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:12.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan's at the top of our class so it's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We could never beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:17.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but stuff like bust size...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:18.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm hungry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have a cup of ramen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not done yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:28.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These three minutes of waiting feel really long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:31.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use this to kill time today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:35.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then your noodles end up soggy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The extra broth for my cup fried soba dried up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:39.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She told me she would be late...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is too late!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let her make a habit of this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.75,0:16:50.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Need to give her a stern dressing down every now and then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the man of the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:54.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:55.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What time do you think it i—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Christmas present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:04.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been cold outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:05.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some hot tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:06.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I do! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,G'day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui's here to save the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You stink of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:17.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to DUI!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I parked the car somewhere and had a drink nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve yet my husband's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plans tonight are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:27.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you go to your parents'\Nplace instead every once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:33.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to sneak in and surprise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:38.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you at your parents' place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:40.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:42.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Running every light on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you shouldn't be breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll log in for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:53.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:54.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:03.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.61,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(556,53)}Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:10.61,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(555,165)}Cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ain't a leftover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't count as a leftover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'Cause I bought one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:21.62,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(416,55)}Nanako Kuroi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.62,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(421,93)}27 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.62,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(144,45)}Single
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:25.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was here last Sunday to buy manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:28.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get why you pay the fare to come here so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's for the points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is pretty excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:31.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:35.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, do you even use the prizes they give?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of stuff is hard to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'd be a waste to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Their value would go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, so that's how it is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:49.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:54.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:55.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:58.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you get shocked by static electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:03.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata's always sitting in front of the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so her body's already full of weird waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I really can't stand winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:11.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I heard you can get shocked just by touching someone's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:12.79,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,411)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:13.59,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,411)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:14.25,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,411)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.13,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,411)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:15.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you two don't really hate each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.01,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(434,421)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:22.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanted to try it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:40.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on the eleventh episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And on this eleventh episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:47.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have some wonderful news you've all been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's sent in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:52.64,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really in it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...lots of passionate letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:57.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...asking for Akira to show up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:57.90,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode, I, Akira Kogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.57,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the assistant Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:00.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.53,0:20:03.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be showing up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.20,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:07.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you to Konata Izumi from\NSaitama along with everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...who sent postcards to Newtype!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Akira-sama's also making an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Like, you're finally showing up in the twelfth episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:20.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in it for, like, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho. Ho. Ho."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...attitude you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:27.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to appear with Akira-sama in the actual show as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:30.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:32.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All you did this week was pick up a handkerchief, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:37.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be thinking you've got\Nwhat it takes to make it in this business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:40.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you can just disappear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:42.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:44.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After that announcement...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't wait for the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You want it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:49.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is probably trembling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, shaking naked in their boots in anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We should treat our fans with care...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:57.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and air it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can grab a thirty minute slot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:58.75,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.92,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be pushing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:03.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:07.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So send any messages to the radio show or the home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:08.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:09.66,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:12.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be bad if I overshadowed the main characters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:15.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It would indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:17.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a tendency for the main character's friends and rivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:21.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to end up more popular than the actual main characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:23.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:24.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:26.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:26.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...talking about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:31.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so full of yourself 'cause you're popular lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:33.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect this to last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:34.18,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:36.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be placing first in the poll
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.02,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.27,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:38.94,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to m—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:50.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next we have a duet from Tsukasa and Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:50.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go up front to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.85,0:21:57.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose a song for them to sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all kinds of songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still an anime song, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:08.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anime songs actually come in handy in these situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:43.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.44,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:20.44,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Really would be so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.40,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,This dream! That dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.40,0:22:26.40,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I have so many dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.36,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:30.37,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:36.33,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The magical pocket makes them come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:40.25,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fly freely through the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:41.13,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:44.25,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Bamboo-copter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.26,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,An! An! An!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:48.76,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:51.55,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Doraemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:09.91,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Homework, clean—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:13.53,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,30)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:13.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:15.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.02,0:23:19.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really hungry one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:21.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it was really late...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:24.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I was wondering if I should eat something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:27.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally decided a little bite would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:29.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I went to the kitchen...
